    https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E19504-01/802-6319/6ia12qkfo/index.html#chapter6-48031

    .. code-block:: c

        struct Elf_Hash {
            uint32_t nbucket;
            uint32_t nchain;
            uint32_t bucket[nbucket];
            uint32_t chain[nchain];
        }

    You can force an ELF to use this type of symbol table by compiling
